[[NBA|NBA]]每年颁发3个荣誉和13个个人奖项，以表彰其球队、球员和教练的成就，不包括授予[[NBA总决赛|NBA总决赛]]胜方的[[NBA總冠軍列表|NBA总冠军奖杯]]。

NBA总冠军奖杯在1947年第一届NBA总决赛之后首次亮相。1964年，该奖杯以[[沃尔特·布朗|沃尔特·布朗]]的名字命名（[[沃爾特·A·布朗冠軍獎盃|沃爾特·A·布朗冠軍獎盃]]），因为布朗在{{tsl|en|Basketball Association of America|全美篮球协会|}}（BAA）和[[国家篮球联盟|国家篮球联盟]]（NBL）合并为NBA的过程中起到了重要作用。<ref name="brown">{{cite web|title=Walter A. Brown|url=http://www.hoophall.com/hall-of-famers/tag/walter-a-brown|accessdate=2008-07-27|publisher=[[奈史密斯篮球名人纪念堂|Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090831074120/http://www.hoophall.com/hall-of-famers/tag/walter-a-brown|archivedate=2009-08-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite encyclopedia|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/404512/National-Basketball-Association|title=NBA|encyclopedia=[[大英百科全书|Encyclopædia Britannica]]|accessdate=2008-07-27|archive-date=2012-03-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66PpU0FET?url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/404512/National-Basketball-Association-NBA/|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{tsl|en|1977 NBA Finals|1977年NBA总决赛|1977}}年，该奖杯外观被重新设计并沿用至今。<ref name="trophy_a">{{cite web|title=Larry O'Brien Championship Trophy|url=http://www.nba.com/lakers/news/trophy_020712.html|accessdate=2008-07-26|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330162941/https://www.nba.com/lakers/news/trophy_020712.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{tsl|en|1984 NBA Finals|1984年NBA总决赛|1984}}年，为了纪念前NBA总裁[[拉里·奥布赖恩|拉里·奥布赖恩]]，NBA总冠军奖杯被重新命名为[[拉里·奧布賴恩冠軍獎盃|拉里·奧布賴恩冠軍獎盃]]。<ref name="trophy_a" /><ref name="trophy_b">{{cite web|title=The trophies|url=http://www.sptimes.com/2003/04/10/Lightning/The_trophies.shtml|accessdate=2008-07-26|date=2003-04-10|work={{tsl|en|St. Petersburg Times||St. Petersburg Times}}|archive-date=2009-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090111064759/http://www.sptimes.com/2003/04/10/Lightning/The_trophies.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="trophy_c">{{cite web|title=NBA Legends Launch 2005 NBA Legends Tour: Destination Finals|url=http://www.nba.com/news/legendstour_050420.html|accessdate=2008-07-26|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66PpWa5Bm?url=http://www.nba.com/news/legendstour_050420.html|archive-date=2012-03-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

NBA在1953年首次推出了2个个人奖项，分别为[[NBA年度最佳新秀|年度最佳新秀]]和[[NBA全明星賽高比拜仁最有價值球員|全明星賽高比拜仁最有價值球員]]。<ref name="allstarrecaps">{{cite web|title=All-Star Game: Year-by-Year Results|url=http://www.nba.com/history/allstar/allstargame_recaps.html|accessdate=2008-07-26|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66PpXxKTu?url=http://www.nba.com/history/allstar/allstargame_recaps.html|archive-date=2012-03-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="roy">{{cite web|title=Rookie of the Year|url=http://www.nba.com/history/awards_rookieofyear.html|accessdate=2008-07-26|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100329231204/http://www.nba.com/history/awards_rookieofyear.html|archive-date=2010-03-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>季后赛只有[[NBA总决赛最有价值球员|总决赛最有价值球员]]这1个个人奖项。[[NBA年度最佳行政人員|年度最佳行政人員]]是唯一一个不是由NBA颁发的奖项，它由《{{tsl|en|Sporting News|体育新闻|}}》颁发，但获得NBA的官方认可。<ref>{{cite web|title=Reports: Baylor wins NBA executive of the year|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=2443842|accessdate=2008-07-24|date=2006-05-14|publisher=ESPN|archive-date=2012-03-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66PpXLS19?url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=2443842|dead-url=no}}</ref>

